name: Dead End (itch) (Steven Paw, 50CI0PATH, Timur Luedemann, Junior17, Miriami)
name_original: Dead End (itch) (Steven Paw, 50CI0PATH, Timur Luedemann, Junior17, Miriami)
description:
A small town seems to be plagued by a curse. 
Children dissappear seemingly right in front of their parents, get stolen fromt their strollers or in their own yard, only to never be seen again.
After yet another person goes missing, a detective decides to look into the case. Navigate your way through an eery little town, which seems to be part of the problem itself.
Can you find all clues?

Use Alt+F4 to end game :)
